long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is not just another browser extension; it's your personal tab manager designed to declutter and organize your browsing experience. Ever found yourself lost amidst a multitude of open tabs? 

Our extension seamlessly groups them for you, ensuring a clean, organized browser interface with just one click. Why navigate chaos when you can have order? 

With "Group My Tabs", you can quickly find what you're looking for, reduce memory usage, and improve your overall productivity. Don't let countless tabs slow you down; install "Group My Tabs" today and experience browsing like never before.

Key Features:
- Group and Name all your tabs with ONE click
- Group tabs per Chrome window opened
- Find corresponding group for newly opened tabs automatically

MORE FEATURES TO COME SOON!!!


This extension is an open source project developed by a community to serve our community. 

Want new feature? Sure, develop it and we will add it in.
Found a Bug and you can fix it? Fork the branch and submit your PR!
Found a Bug and can't fix it or you wish this extension had new feature? Head into Support section and let us know, we will try to fix it ASAP!!
